<script type="text/javascript" src="http://newsimg.5054399.com/static/simpleztmicro/js/jquery.SuperSlide.2.1.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(".tab span").click(function () {
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("span").removeClass("on");
        $(".tabcon .list0").hide().eq($(this).index()).show();
        var display = $('#gongao').css('display');
        if (display == 'none') {
            $("#gengduo").hide();
        } else {
            $("#gengduo").show();
        }
    });
    //»î¶¯ÂÖ²¥Ïà¹Ø
    var curban = 0;
    $(".imgtit li").bind("mouseenter", function () {
        curban = $(this).index();
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
        $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
    });
    var imgboxScroll;
    $(document).ready(function () {
        imgboxScroll = setInterval(function () { $(".imgtit em.nbtn").click(); }, 3000);
    });
    $(".imgbox,.imgtit").mouseenter(function () {
        clearInterval(imgboxScroll);
    })
    $(".imgbox,.imgtit").mouseleave(function () {
        imgboxScroll = setInterval(function () { $(".imgtit em.nbtn").click(); }, 3000)
    })
    $(".splist .sp").hover(function () {
        $(this).find(".cover").toggleClass("cover1");
    });
    if ($(".titbox li").length) {
        $(".imgtit .pbtn").click(function () { scrollTop(); });
        $(".imgtit .nbtn").click(function () { scrollDown(); });
        var scrollban = $(".titbox .tits");
        var baniscol = parseInt(scrollban.find("li").css("height"));
        var bansnum = scrollban.children().length;
        var inum = 1;//Ò»´Î¹ö¶¯¸öÊý
        var banmarginL = 0;
        var banmaxMagin = -baniscol * (bansnum - 4);
        if ($(".titbox li").length < 4) {
            banmaxMagin = 0;
        }
        function scrollDown() {
            if (banmarginL > banmaxMagin) {
                banmarginL = banmarginL - baniscol * inum;
                if (curban == bansnum) {
                    curban = 0;
                } else curban++;
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
            } else {
                if (curban == bansnum - 1) {
                    curban = 0;
                    banmarginL = 0;
                    scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                } else curban++;
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            }
        }
        function scrollTop() {
            if (banmarginL == 0) {
                if (curban == 0) {
                    curban = bansnum - 1;
                    banmarginL = banmaxMagin;
                } else if (curban < 4) {
                    curban--;
                    banmarginL = 0;
                } else {
                    curban--;
                    banmarginL = banmarginL + baniscol * inum;
                }
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            } else {
                curban--;
                banmarginL = banmarginL + baniscol * inum;
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            }
        }
    }


    //½ÇÉ«ÂÖ²¥Ïà¹Ø
    var currole = 0;
    $(".roletab li").click(function () {
        currole = $(this).index();
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
        $(".rolecon .item").hide().eq(currole).show();
    });
    if ($(".roletab ul li").length > 4) {
        $(".roletab .prev").hide();
        $(".roletab .next").show();
        $(".roletab .prev").click(function () { scrollLeft(); });
        $(".roletab .next").click(function () { scrollRight(); });
        var scrollImg = $(".roletab ul");
        var iwidth = parseInt(scrollImg.find("li").css("width"));
        var imargin = parseInt(scrollImg.find("li").css("margin-right"));
        var iscol = iwidth + imargin;
        var snum = scrollImg.children().length;
        var inum = 1;//Ò»´Î¹ö¶¯¸öÊý
        var marginL = 0;
        var maxMagin = -iscol * (snum - 4);
        function scrollRight() {
            if (marginL > maxMagin) {
                marginL = marginL - iscol * inum;
                scrollImg.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-left": marginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".roletab .prev").show();
                if (marginL == maxMagin) {
                    $(".roletab .next").hide();
                }
            } else {
                $(".roletab .next").hide();
            }
        }
        function scrollLeft() {
            if (marginL < 0) {
                marginL = marginL + iscol * inum;
                scrollImg.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-left": marginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".roletab .next").show();
                if (marginL == 0) {
                    $(".roletab .prev").hide();
                }
            } else $(".roletab .prev").hide();
        }
    } else {
        $(".roletab .prev,.roletab .next").hide();
    }


    $(".splist .sp").hover(function () {
        $(this).find(".cover").toggleClass("cover1");
    });
    // ÂÖ²¥Í¼
    if ($('.scroll-main').length > 0) {
        $(".scroll-main").slide({
            mainCell: ".scroll-cont ul",
            autoPlay: true,
            titCell: ".s-hd a",
            interTime: 5000,
            effect: "left"
        });
    }
    //²à±ßÒþ²Ø
    $(document).ready(function () {
        autoSetResizellHide();
        $(window).resize(function () {
            autoSetResizellHide();
        });
        $(window).scroll(function () {
            autoSetResizellHide();
        });
    });
    function autoSetResizellHide() {
        var fix = $(".fix");
        if ($(window).width() < 1024) {
            fix.hide();
        } else {
            $(window).scroll(function () {
                var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
                var fix = $(".fix");
                if (scrollTop > 100) {
                    fix.show();
                } else {
                    fix.hide();
                }
            })
        }
    }

<script type="text/javascript">
    $(".tab span").click(function () {
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("span").removeClass("on");
        $(".tabcon .list0").hide().eq($(this).index()).show();
        var display = $('#gongao').css('display');
        if (display == 'none') {
            $("#gengduo").hide();
        } else {
            $("#gengduo").show();
        }
    });
    //»î¶¯ÂÖ²¥Ïà¹Ø
    var curban = 0;
    $(".imgtit li").bind("mouseenter", function () {
        curban = $(this).index();
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
        $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
    });
    var imgboxScroll;
    $(document).ready(function () {
        imgboxScroll = setInterval(function () { $(".imgtit em.nbtn").click(); }, 3000);
    });
    $(".imgbox,.imgtit").mouseenter(function () {
        clearInterval(imgboxScroll);
    })
    $(".imgbox,.imgtit").mouseleave(function () {
        imgboxScroll = setInterval(function () { $(".imgtit em.nbtn").click(); }, 3000)
    })
    $(".splist .sp").hover(function () {
        $(this).find(".cover").toggleClass("cover1");
    });
    if ($(".titbox li").length) {
        $(".imgtit .pbtn").click(function () { scrollTop(); });
        $(".imgtit .nbtn").click(function () { scrollDown(); });
        var scrollban = $(".titbox .tits");
        var baniscol = parseInt(scrollban.find("li").css("height"));
        var bansnum = scrollban.children().length;
        var inum = 1;//Ò»´Î¹ö¶¯¸öÊý
        var banmarginL = 0;
        var banmaxMagin = -baniscol * (bansnum - 4);
        if ($(".titbox li").length < 4) {
            banmaxMagin = 0;
        }
        function scrollDown() {
            if (banmarginL > banmaxMagin) {
                banmarginL = banmarginL - baniscol * inum;
                if (curban == bansnum) {
                    curban = 0;
                } else curban++;
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
            } else {
                if (curban == bansnum - 1) {
                    curban = 0;
                    banmarginL = 0;
                    scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                } else curban++;
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            }
        }
        function scrollTop() {
            if (banmarginL == 0) {
                if (curban == 0) {
                    curban = bansnum - 1;
                    banmarginL = banmaxMagin;
                } else if (curban < 4) {
                    curban--;
                    banmarginL = 0;
                } else {
                    curban--;
                    banmarginL = banmarginL + baniscol * inum;
                }
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            } else {
                curban--;
                banmarginL = banmarginL + baniscol * inum;
                scrollban.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-top": banmarginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".titbox li").eq(curban).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
                $(".imgbox li").hide().eq(curban).show();
            }
        }
    }


    //½ÇÉ«ÂÖ²¥Ïà¹Ø
    var currole = 0;
    $(".roletab li").click(function () {
        currole = $(this).index();
        $(this).addClass("on").siblings("li").removeClass("on");
        $(".rolecon .item").hide().eq(currole).show();
    });
    if ($(".roletab ul li").length > 4) {
        $(".roletab .prev").hide();
        $(".roletab .next").show();
        $(".roletab .prev").click(function () { scrollLeft(); });
        $(".roletab .next").click(function () { scrollRight(); });
        var scrollImg = $(".roletab ul");
        var iwidth = parseInt(scrollImg.find("li").css("width"));
        var imargin = parseInt(scrollImg.find("li").css("margin-right"));
        var iscol = iwidth + imargin;
        var snum = scrollImg.children().length;
        var inum = 1;//Ò»´Î¹ö¶¯¸öÊý
        var marginL = 0;
        var maxMagin = -iscol * (snum - 4);
        function scrollRight() {
            if (marginL > maxMagin) {
                marginL = marginL - iscol * inum;
                scrollImg.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-left": marginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".roletab .prev").show();
                if (marginL == maxMagin) {
                    $(".roletab .next").hide();
                }
            } else {
                $(".roletab .next").hide();
            }
        }
        function scrollLeft() {
            if (marginL < 0) {
                marginL = marginL + iscol * inum;
                scrollImg.stop(true, true).animate({ "margin-left": marginL + "px" }, 500);
                $(".roletab .next").show();
                if (marginL == 0) {
                    $(".roletab .prev").hide();
                }
            } else $(".roletab .prev").hide();
        }
    } else {
        $(".roletab .prev,.roletab .next").hide();
    }


    $(".splist .sp").hover(function () {
        $(this).find(".cover").toggleClass("cover1");
    });
    // ÂÖ²¥Í¼
    if ($('.scroll-main').length > 0) {
        $(".scroll-main").slide({
            mainCell: ".scroll-cont ul",
            autoPlay: true,
            titCell: ".s-hd a",
            interTime: 5000,
            effect: "left"
        });
    }
    //²à±ßÒþ²Ø
    $(document).ready(function () {
        autoSetResizellHide();
        $(window).resize(function () {
            autoSetResizellHide();
        });
        $(window).scroll(function () {
            autoSetResizellHide();
        });
    });
    function autoSetResizellHide() {
        var fix = $(".fix");
        if ($(window).width() < 1024) {
            fix.hide();
        } else {
            $(window).scroll(function () {
                var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
                var fix = $(".fix");
                if (scrollTop > 100) {
                    fix.show();
                } else {
                    fix.hide();
                }
            })
        }
    }

</script>

function init_data(pf){
	   $("#pp1").attr("class","all");
	   $("#pp2").attr("class","new");
	   $("#pp3").attr("class","hot");

	      $("#pp1").attr("class","all-on");

	      $("#pp3").attr("class","hot-on");

	   }

	     wscroll();

$(document).ready(function(){
    if(typeof(possible_search_words)!="undefined"){ 
        var sic = document.getElementById("smart_input"); 
        function jsrnd(n,m){var c = m-n+1;return Math.floor(Math.random() * c + n);}
        var jsrndbum = jsrnd(0,possible_search_words.length-1);
        var defaultsearch = possible_search_words[jsrndbum];
        if(defaultsearch){
            sic.value = defaultsearch;
            sic.onfocus = function(){if(sic.value == defaultsearch){sic.value='';}};
            sic.onblur = function(){if(sic.value == ''){sic.value=defaultsearch;}};
            sic.placeholder = defaultsearch;
        }
    }
});

$(document).ready(function(){
    if(typeof(possible_search_words)!="undefined"){ 
        var sic = document.getElementById("smart_input"); 
        function jsrnd(n,m){var c = m-n+1;return Math.floor(Math.random() * c + n);}
        var jsrndbum = jsrnd(0,possible_search_words.length-1);
        var defaultsearch = possible_search_words[jsrndbum];
        if(defaultsearch){
            sic.value = defaultsearch;
            sic.onfocus = function(){if(sic.value == defaultsearch){sic.value='';}};
            sic.onblur = function(){if(sic.value == ''){sic.value=defaultsearch;}};
            sic.placeholder = defaultsearch;
        }
    }
});

 function check_search(node,default_value){
    var default_color = '#000';
    var default_value = default_value;
    node.find('input[name="q"]').val(default_value);
    node.find("input[name='q']").focus(function(){
      if($(this).val()==default_value){
        $(this).val("");
        default_color = $(this).css("color");
        $(this).css("color",default_color);
      }
    }).blur(function(){
      if($.trim($(this).val())==''){
        $(this).css("color",default_color)
        $(this).val(default_value);
      }
    })
}  
function searchp(flag){
        var text = $("#form1").find("input[name='q']");
        var search_value = $.trim(text.val());
        if(search_value==default_value || search_value==''){
          alert(default_value);
          text.focus();
          return false;
        }else{              
          if(flag==2){
			  window.open('http://news.4399.com/seer/ss.php?q='+search_value,'_blank');
		   }else{
			  window.open('http://news.4399.com/seer/search.php?q='+search_value,'_blank');
		   }
        }
}
  $("#form1").find("input[name='q']").bind('keypress',function(event){
      if(event.keyCode == "13"){
        searchp(1);
      }
   });

<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function(){
    if(typeof(possible_search_words)!="undefined"){ 
        var sic = document.getElementById("smart_input"); 
        function jsrnd(n,m){var c = m-n+1;return Math.floor(Math.random() * c + n);}
        var jsrndbum = jsrnd(0,possible_search_words.length-1);
        var defaultsearch = possible_search_words[jsrndbum];
        if(defaultsearch){
            sic.value = defaultsearch;
            sic.onfocus = function(){if(sic.value == defaultsearch){sic.value='';}};
            sic.onblur = function(){if(sic.value == ''){sic.value=defaultsearch;}};
            sic.placeholder = defaultsearch;
        }
    }
});

        var sic = document.getElementById("smart_input"); 
        function jsrnd(n,m){var c = m-n+1;return Math.floor(Math.random() * c + n);}
        var jsrndbum = jsrnd(0,possible_search_words.length-1);
        var defaultsearch = possible_search_words[jsrndbum];
        if(defaultsearch){
            sic.value = defaultsearch;
            sic.onfocus = function(){if(sic.value == defaultsearch){sic.value='';}};
            sic.onblur = function(){if(sic.value == ''){sic.value=defaultsearch;}};
            sic.placeholder = defaultsearch;
        }
    }
});
</script>			<center>

    function hand_url(){
      var searchString = location.search;
      var pos = searchString.indexOf ("?");
      if (pos == 0){
        var thislocation = document.location.href;
        var urls = thislocation.split("?");
        var thisurl = urls[0];
        window.location.href = thisurl;
      }
    }
    hand_url();

$(document).ready(function(){
    if(typeof(possible_search_words)!="undefined"){ 
        var sic = document.getElementById("smart_input"); 
        function jsrnd(n,m){var c = m-n+1;return Math.floor(Math.random() * c + n);}
        var jsrndbum = jsrnd(0,possible_search_words.length-1);
        var defaultsearch = possible_search_words[jsrndbum];
        if(defaultsearch){
            sic.value = defaultsearch;
            sic.onfocus = function(){if(sic.value == defaultsearch){sic.value='';}};
            sic.onblur = function(){if(sic.value == ''){sic.value=defaultsearch;}};
            sic.placeholder = defaultsearch;
        }
    }
});

<script>
init();
function go_to(div,top){
	var top = parseInt(div.offset().top) - (top || 0);
	window.scrollTo(0,top);
	window.event && (window.event.returnValue = false);
	return false;
}
go_to($('.game_c'),4);
function page_init(pagecount){
	var cur = 1;
	var cur_pre;
	var cur_next;
	$('#top_page #pre').click(function(){
		cur_pre  = cur-1;
		if (cur_pre<=0) cur_pre = 1;
		cur = cur_pre;
		$('#top_ui li:[rel]').hide();
		$('#top_ui li:[rel='+cur+']').show();
		$('#page_cur').html(cur);
		return false;
	});

	$('#top_page #next').click(function(){
		cur_next  = cur+1;
		if (cur_next>pagecount) cur_next = pagecount;
		cur = cur_next;

		$('#top_ui li:[rel]').hide();
		$('#top_ui li:[rel='+cur+']').show();
		$('#page_cur').html(cur);
		return false;
	});
}
getFlower('hero_sh',$('em[aid]'));
function getFlower(zt,ems){
	var ids = [];
	ems.each(function(){
		ids.push($(this).attr('aid'));
	});

	var max = 3;
	$.ajax({
		type : "GET",
		url : 'http://huodong3.4399.com/comm/arc_vote/get.php?zt='+zt+'&aids='+ids.join(',')+'&max='+max+'&r='+Math.random()+'&callback?',
		dataType : "jsonp",
		jsonp: 'callback',
		success : function(result){
			if(!result) return;
			if(result.status == 'ok'){
				ems.each(function(index){
					var cnt = 0;
					for(var i=0;i<max;i++){
						cnt += parseInt(result.data[index][i]);
					}
					$(this).html(cnt.toString());
				});
			}
		}
	});
}
</script>

var xb_length = $("#xjxbList ul").length;
var xb_pos = 0;
$('#changebtn').click(function(){
	xb_pos++;
	if(xb_pos>=xb_length) xb_pos=0;
	$("#xjxbList ul").hide().filter(":eq("+xb_pos+")").show().find("img[lz_src]").attr("src",function(){
		var src = $(this).attr("lz_src");
		$(this).removeClass("lz_src");
		return src;

	});
	return false;
});
